entries.femaleVariant: Hey, so, when I play a lot, my fingers hurt. What do I do to stop them?
Where?!
Hey, relax, why so tense? Steve's helpin' me out. He'll be back in two hours tops, choom.
You don't. Metal strings cut into your fingertips, make 'em sore â€“ just how it is.
Oh...
I decide when the punk comes, goes, what he does. Not you.
He won't come back empty-handed.
Uhhh, just... out for a sec. Be back soon.
Back inside, now! Not about to let you go out, do who knows what, y'hear?
Fuck's sake! D'you swipe my keys again?
Inside! Now, you shit!
Get your own wheels, deadbeat. An' stay the hell away from my boy.
Hey, I'm talkin' to you!
The fuck you starin' at? You got somethin' to say?
Back inside, I said, shit-for-brains! What the hell you waitin' for?
Don't worry. Play long enough and you'll get calluses. Start hittin' those frets like hammers. Won't hurt a bit.
I was gonna get coated strings.
Leave 'im alone. And watch that tone.
The fuck you want?
Even saved up, but... my mom needed stuff for the house. Gave it to her.
Get the fuck outta my face. Think I'm scared? You're another bum like the rest of us.
Two hours. And you hand me those eddies soon as you come through the door.
All right, Dad.
Who the fuck knows. Another tramp. All look the same to me.
Prolly a yapper.
What're you gonna do? Can't catch me, can't force me.
Can barely stand on your own two feet.
Maybe Steve wouldn't be so eager to ghost outta his home if it wasn't a drunk tank.
Heh, you think your place is any better?
Maybe if he had a real home, he'd stay.
Leave the kid alone.
Calm down. I'm paying him.
What d'you think you're doin', you little shit?
Goin' out.
Wanna try me? Go ahead.
Who the hell's that?
I'm going. That's that.
I don't got a kid.
Keep this shit up, you won't have one either.
Goddamn corps want us shakin' in our shorts, twenty-four seven.
My Steve started talkin' to 'er. Now he bangs on that damn guitar night an' day.
entries.maleVariant: My Steve started talkin' to 'im. Now he bangs on that damn guitar all night an' day.

entries.femaleVariant: Better whip that boy in line.
I don't have time for this shit.
